OL,3,CCCTV shows thief emerge from hiding in
OL,4,Ccharity shop before stealing cash
OL,6,FA thief, who hid inside a charity
OL,7,Fshop, as it closed, before stealing
OL,8,Fseveral items and #520 from the safe,
OL,9,Fhas been jailed less than 48 hours
OL,10,Fafter the incident took place.
OL,12,FThe break-in, on the High Street in
OL,13,FMaidstone, Kent, was reported to
OL,14,Fpolice on the morning of Wednesday 4
OL,15,FFebruary 2026.
OL,17,FUsing CCTV - officers were able to
OL,18,Fquickly identify the suspect, and
OL,19,Farrested a man at an address in
OL,20,FMaidstone, less than three hours after
OL,21,Fthe report was made.
