OL,6,FDanny Crawley, 44, from Abbey Wood in
OL,7,FLondon was arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fburglary and also arrested for
OL,9,Fbreaching a restraining order, as he
OL,10,Fwas banned from the address he was
OL,11,Ffound in.
OL,13,FHe was charged later that day and
OL,14,Fappeared in Medway Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fon Thursday 5 February, where he
OL,16,Fpleaded guilty.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced to 35 weeks in prison
OL,19,Fand ordered to pay #500 compensation.
