OL,6,FInsp Steve Kent from the Maidstone
OL,7,FCommunity Safety Unit said: "Officers
OL,8,Futilised their strong local knowledge
OL,9,Fto quickly identify and arrest Crawley.
OL,11,F"This type of crime has a real impact,
OL,12,Fnot just on the businesses affected
OL,13,Fbut on the wider community.
OL,15,F"Incidents like this show just how
OL,16,Fimportant beat officers are. They have
OL,17,Fa wealth of knowledge of their patch
OL,18,Fand are there to protect residents and
OL,19,Fbusinesses as well as taking action
OL,20,Fagainst offenders."
